Ndugu zangu, muiteganye, munhu yoyose mgati mmwenu sekeye na moyo wihile wabule uhuwilo, yamuleke Mulungu yeli ngima.
Mbali lutizaneni moyo chila siku, lusita luja lusita lujitangigwa "Diyelo," muladi sekemwize hata imwe wenu yamuuligwe moyo kwa uvwizi wa uhasanyi.
Kwaviya cheye chiwa wanhu woiting'hana na Chilisito, one muhala chiwamha goya uhuwilo wetu wa mwanduso mbaka kuuhelelo.
Fana Maandiko Yelile viyolonga, "Diyelo one muhahulika dizi jake, sekemuwe na mizoyo yenu midala fana viya viya viyawatendile muna isiku ya kuibasula Mulungu."
