Kwaviya hanhu hamwenga muna Yamaandiko Yelile kalonga mbuli ya siku ya saba vino, "Na muna isiku ya saba, Mulungu kahumula kulawa kuna usang'hano wake wose."
Maabaho Mulungu kalonga iviya, "Whazakwingila bule muna ikaye yangu ya kuhumula."
Ivo viyagala wazi kuwa wanhu wamwenga wezakwingila muna ichiheleto, na waja wa mwanduso wowahulike Mbuli Inogile hawadahile kwingila muna ichiheleto kwaviya hawamtegeleze Mulungu.
