Na lagano jangu hawizakuwa fana diyatendile na wasaho zawo baho viniawagwilile mkono niwalave muna isi ya Misili. Kwaviya wawo hawasamhile lagano jangu, na niye niwalaga, niwaleka kaidi, Mndewa kolonga.
